'''Gre Shev'starn''' was a city on the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. 

It was located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] western continent, southeast of [[Odve'starn]]. The city of [[Urval'starn]] was nearby to the east.

